a1 1
.\"	$OpenBSD$
d23 1
a23 1
.Nd Geode LX Security Block device
d39 4
d44 4
a47 1
.Xr random 4
d61 3
a63 2
driver does not yet use the AES acceleration provided by the security block;
it only uses the random number generator.
